name: Vintage
description: Great little purse with clutch style handles makes for a great evening bag or weekend bag as well. Purse measures 10" in length X 9.5" wide. Colors are....base:bright pink, body:bright pink & bright vintage green. Top portion of purse has a nice flare happening....Enjoy your day!

name: Rectangle Bag
description: Zippered rectangle bag! Fabric is bluish gray in color with interesting lines that run throughout the fabric. Great for holding straight knitting needles,circulars,notions or whatever your heart desires! Bag measures 11.5" in width X 4.5" in length...Enjoy your day!

name: The Rose Garden
description: I love to knit & felt up these purses, so much fun! This would be great for an evening out or a fun running around weekend bag. Purse measures 10.5" wide X 9" in length with clutch style handles. Colors are....base is red, body is a multi of red/pink, clutch portion is cream with a fern green colored flower (pink & cream bobbles for center of flower).....Enjoy your day!

name: Autumn Bag
description: Fresh off the knitting needles felted purse, picture does not do it justice! Purse measures 13" wide X 9" long with two tortoise shell colored handles about 6" in diameter. Body of purse is knitted in a 3 stripe pattern in shades of brown's (middle stripe is a heathered brown with green specks)and cream colored inserts for handles. Great little bag....Enjoy your day!

name: My Funny Tote
description: Fresh off the knitting needles...picture does not do it justice. Has an interesting shape...Bag measures 17" L X 12 1/2" W. Stripe sequence done in shades of pinks & wine colors, accessorized with a felted green flower. Handle measures about 22" in length....Enjoy your day!
